FBIS4-38979 "drsov107_l_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-107 Daily Report 1 Jun 1994 Kyrgyzstan Commission Formed To Help Bankrupt Workers Commission Formed To Help Bankrupt Workers LD0206105594 Bishkek Kyrgyz Radio First Program Network in Russian 2300 GMT 1 Jun 94 LD0206105594 Bishkek Kyrgyz Radio First Program Network Russian BFN [Text] The republican Union of Entrepreneurs has set up a special commission to collect information on enterprises which are made bankrupt and are subject to liquidation. The commission's task is to help the leaders of such enterprises to prepare documents on the enterprises' inability to function and their proposals on reorganization. The commission intends to address a letter to the president of Kyrgyzstan and establish cooperation with the state commission on reorganizing and liquidating unprofitable enterprises.
